<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Content/css/ling.css">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    @RenderSection("headscripts", required: false)
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-inner">
            <img src="@ViewBag.Logo" class="ling-logo">
            <ul class="u-header">
                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Request["MenuId"]))
                {
                    Html.RenderAction("_DescMenu", "_Layout");
                }
                else
                {
                    Html.RenderAction("_Menu", "_Layout", new { name = ViewBag.Name });
                }
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    @RenderBody()
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="wrap">
            <p><a href="/Partner">合作伙伴</a></p>
            <p>健康游戏忠告：抵制不良游戏，拒绝盗版游戏。注意自我保护，谨防受骗上当。适度游戏益脑，沉迷游戏伤身。合理安排时间，享受健康生活</p>
            <p><i></i>COPYRIGHT © 2016 杭州匀腾网络科技有限公司 ALL RIGHTS RESERVED</p>
            <p>
                <a target="_blank" href="http://www.beian.gov.cn/portal/registerSystemInfo?recordcode=33010602006168">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/beian.png" />浙公网安备 33010602006168号
                </a>
            </p> 
        </div>
    </div>
    @{Html.RenderAction("_RigthFloat", "_Layout");}

    <script src="/Scripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
    @RenderSection("scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
